<l:h1>Buying a Factory<l:/h1>  <l:eu_i_factory>
It may be necessary to build a factory in an area far from the nearest factory area, or to expand an existing factory's capacity. When you buy a factory, you get a capacity of 10 Pu's at a price of 12 and you will see the factory capacity raise in the factory area.
You can buy sea-factories in any sea-area neighboring one of your land-areas, unless this sea-area is under control by another country.
You buy factories by draging the factory icon from the <l:ha_equipment> window to the desired area.


<l:h1>Destroying a Factory<l:/h1>
It may be necessary to destroy a factory in an area if the enemy is about to conquer it. You destroy a factory the following way:
1. Open the factory area window.
2. Select the factory icon.
3. Choose the <l:ha_destroy_f> item at the Game menu.
4. The factory is destroyed.
Remember: Never let the enemy take over a factory!








